-- Samaras to Be Sworn in as Greek Prime Minister Today
-- B y   M a r c u s   B e n s a s s o n   a n d   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 2012-06-20T11:45:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/samaras-to-be-sworn-in-as-greek-premier-today-official-says.html
Antonis Samaras, leader of  Greece ’s
New Democracy party, will be sworn in today as premier of the
country’s new coalition government, a New Democracy official
told reporters in Athens.  President Karolos Papoulias will swear in Samaras after
Samaras today visits him to brief him on the results of his
mandate to form a government, said the official, who declined to
be named.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marcus Bensasson in Athens at 
